ng contact between the committee members and the research teamsthe efficient practical organisationThe quality of the attendance and the support from the community have allowed Moriond to have a visible impacton this community, since :results and ideas are more easily discussed than in larger conferences, often by the young physicists directlyinvolvedyoung physicists giving the first #|2
